      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THREENTWO (3) gets a much better draw than last start and cam take advantage of that. Should be hitting peak fitness now and finds a winnable assignment. The recent form of THE BLINGSTER (6) may not leap off the page but he has been tackling stronger company since a placing here three back and should find this more to his liking. RAINBOW GAMBLER (8) continues to race well. Had a win at this venue two runs ago before finishing second at his latest appearance at Redcliffe. Shouldn't spend a penny from this draw and sprint lane may come in handy. ICANANDIWILL (9) has improved with each start so far this time in. Wasn't beaten all that far two runs back then got the win she deserved last time out at Redcliffe, arriving 2.7 metres ahead of the runner-up. Gets the same draw and could go on with it.",
